{"type": "article", "id": 42638, "title": "想收藏赖特的建筑模型？试试这本立体书｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-07-03T23:09:47Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 42010, "name": "LEHFT"}, {"id": 42011, "name": "haaz"}, {"id": 42012, "name": "Studio Caserne"}, {"id": 32194, "name": "Hochu rayu"}, {"id": 42013, "name": "Avanaa"}, {"id": 34053, "name": "Frank Lloyd Wright"}, {"id": 42014, "name": "Marc Hagan-Guirey"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 248, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170703212322GxrblzKuHE7q6LmV.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Frank Lloyd Wright Paper Models by Marc Hagan-Guirey</h3><p>今年是著名的美国建筑师弗兰克·劳埃德·赖特（Frank Lloyd Wright）诞辰 150 周年，纽约 MoMA 为此正在举办赖特的个人大型主题展。如果你更倾向于用另一种方式近距离欣赏他的作品，由英国纸艺家 Marc Hagan-Guirey 出版的剪纸书可以满足你的收藏欲。根据指示，你就能将一张薄薄的纸打造成流水别墅、罗比住宅、东京帝国饭店在内的 14 座建筑纸模。该书将于 7 月 25 日开始发售，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Frank-Lloyd-Wright-Paper-Models/dp/1786270064/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>预定，售价为 20.39 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212356V8ElpDLUbXB159PA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212355Oc4ZHuwxltGbh91q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212356QnodqCWH3wgv1XaY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212356czoBJvsTbPdkwnpL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212357VfuMpHmY5dSKkJWn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.540833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>My Drawing Board by Benjamin Benais</h3><p>在桌上画画时，我们很容易维持伏案的姿势，长久下去就会造成颈椎和腰椎的不适。为了帮助创意人士更好地完成工作，法国设计师 Benjamin Benais 设计了一款与电脑支架颇为相似的折叠式画板，可以直接带去户外使用。除了调整姿势以外，画板顶部还配备了多个用来收纳文具的洞眼和凹槽，图纸也可以直接存储在木板中。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/306675580/my-drawing-board-ergonomic-and-functional-drawing\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 139 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212416FBNmkyrQMPhXV4uS.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.553125\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212415LDOiKNd1jp8EHz2f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.719118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212415ZNJm7nqa0UF6SPiO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212415z3EpLunBjeOcSoWg.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212415yUuqDXrlNm5P1ong.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860294\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>All Black Edition by LEHFT</h3><p>来自墨尔本的 <a href=\"https://www.lehft.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LEHFT</a> 是一个以“简约但不随大流”为设计宗旨的中性腕表品牌，根据 1 和 7 两个时刻度将表面分为深浅不一的两部分是它最标志性的特色。腕表本身采用的是瑞士朗达的石英机芯，表盘则由 PVD 涂层的不锈钢制成，最后辅以小牛皮皮带。你可以通过官方网站购买到这些腕表，售价为 249 澳元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212648iOp5U8QXGxMZKzT3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212647CmPGTQE5zyDintRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212647XNDuBbtkMHq2WVzP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707032126479gaRA0uVGxDlpqIi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.515152\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Laurel toys by haaz</h3><p>2012 年成立的 haaz 是坐落在东京白金台的一间小型设计工坊，经营各类手工打造的家具以及装饰品。最近，他们砍下了种植在庭院内的月桂树枝，将它们制作成一组朴实又可爱的木质玩具。其中既有由半圆形木块构成的帆船、汽车和小动物，也有以传统工艺制成、看起来像是会动的蛇。这些<a href=\"http://www.haaz.co.jp/others_laureltoys.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">月桂树玩具</a>每款仅有一件，售价为 1620 日元，除了实体店之外，仅限邮件订购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212539VeXE1R7BWvxzwrdZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.784286\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212539WUwN1vVXlDsuHtBx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212539EhMZKg7wx50NPaH3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.458571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Helmfon by Hochu rayu</h3><p>想要全身心地投入工作中不受干扰，光有一副普通的降噪耳机或许并不够——至少在乌克兰设计公司 <a href=\"http://hochurayu.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hochu rayu</a> 看来，一个特大号的降噪头盔能让你彻底开启防干扰模式。这款名为 Helmfon 的头盔不光能阻隔外部噪音，它还内置了麦克风、扬声器以及用来放置手机的收纳空间，因此人们可以在同一个会议室内各自独立进行电话会议。虽然团队号称头盔的夸张造型能确保上班族将实现集中到眼前的工作，但长期保持同一姿势以及它本身的重量都会对颈椎造成一定的负担。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707032124510aBVcbUSFe3Iv1ZY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212448Zk0ljAPQ3aF7o8en.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707032124510RrJBDFQMT2xjWYz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017070321244824Nn6GkrQ5s9lO3o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Avanaa by Studio Caserne</h3><p>加拿大平面设计工作室 <a href=\"http://studiocaserne.ca/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studio Caserne</a> 为蒙特利尔的 bean-to-bar 巧克力公司 Avanaa 设计了一组简洁而温暖的包装。包装正面采用了出自插画家 Cécile Gariépy 之笔的可可豆农形象，图案上方覆盖了醒目的原产地名，借此强调它们的来源以及农民的辛勤劳动。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707032125132uGWSUrischZLkOw.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212513k4lhi2pKJV1TUftD.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170703212513ltGUqM7ZsSO92Qda.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div>"}